Building (linux.student.cs.uwaterloo.ca)
========================================


Clone repo and compile commands within terminal:
---------------------------------------------------------
git clone https://git.uwaterloo.ca/dduranro/kernel.git
cd kernel
git checkout 
make
---------------------------------------------------------

This will produce kernel3.img which should be deployed to the RPi and run. 
See the course web page for deployment instructions.

Upon running, no other user input is needed. 
The program will dynamically update the console with an idle time percentage
The program will also display various clock clients with a TID, delay interval, and number of delays.

